    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite 10 of 13 credibility factors assessed below required levels and 4 factors not assessed, the package is accepted for submission as a credibility argument under the low-assurance pathway. The ValidationResults demonstrate mesh convergence (GCI < 2%) and experimental agreement within 15% for the primary QoI. Monte Carlo UQ confirms the 95th percentile hemolysis index remains below clinical threshold. The Claim node (https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-credibility) is richly described and references all relevant assessment activities; the overall credibility argument is considered sufficient for the declared assurance level.",
